=== Example 010: Basic which command ===
Using backticks to call which with a fixed PATH:
which alpha: test_which_bin/alpha

which with a fixed command set:
alpha: test_which_bin/alpha
beta: test_which_bin/beta
gamma: test_which_bin/gamma

which with all matches (-a):
test_which_bin/alpha

which with non-existent command:
Command not found
